Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:48.05,Main,Enta,0,0,0,,我  得救了吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:48.89,Main,Kazuki,0,0,0,,悠…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:51.03,Main,Toi,0,0,0,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.55,0:21:54.20,Main,Toi,0,0,0,,我如果是你  也会选择救阵内
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:58.21,Main,Toi,0,0,0,,但是我已经累了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:00.71,Main,Kazuki,0,0,0,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:04.13,Main,Otter,0,0,0,,胡说！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:08.97,Main,Otter,0,0,0,,来吧  把这个世界上的联系全部切断
